txt.en: Anborn can be found in Haerondir.\n\nYou should speak with Anborn.
Anborn has asked for help filling water-skins in Haerondir.\n\nFirst, find an empty bucket to fill with water.
Anborn has asked for help filling water-skins in Haerondir.\n\nFill the empty bucket with water at the Haerondir water source.
Anborn has asked for help filling water-skins in Haerondir.\n\nUse the full bucket to fill water-skins.
Anborn has asked for help packing up Haerondir supplies for the march.\n\nYou should collect weapons from weapon racks and collect armour from barrels.
Fill the empty bucket at Haerondir water source ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'Thank you, [placeholder]. Every bit of help counts, even if it's something simple.\n\n'The Rangers are now prepared to join the Host of the West in their march to the Black Gate. However, there is still plenty to be done in the Wastes before that. Gladhir and Maendal may have leads for you.'

â€˜One last chore remains in Haerondir before we send you out further into The Wastes. We have supplies here that would be useful to the Camp of the Host, but they need to be gathered before we continue the march. There's armour and weapons to be gathered, and water-skins to be filled. Can I ask you to make a sweep of Haerondir and attend to this? I know it is a bit menial for such a skilled [placeholder], but we are woefully short-handed.'
Fill Bucket at Haerondir Water Source
Anborn requires your help gathering what supplies remain in Haerondir to aid the Host of the West's march to the Black Gate.
